@page "/line-privacy-policy"

<div class="policy-wrapper">
    <div class="policy-card">
        <div class="policy-header">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="20" fill="#06C755" />
                <path d="M20 8C13.4 8 8 12.6 8 18.2C8 23.2 12.4 27.4 18.4 28.2L19.2 30.8C19.4 31.4 20.2 31.4 20.6 30.8L22.2 28.2C28 27.2 32 23.1 32 18.2C32 12.6 26.6 8 20 8Z" fill="white"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
                <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="policy-meta">CNU LINE Login &nbsp;|&nbsp; Effective from January 1, 2025</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section>
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
                CNU Chatbot Management System ("the Application") is a system developed by Chalermkarnchana University (CNU)
                to allow users to log in via a LINE account and conveniently use the Chatbot management functions.
                We place great importance on user privacy and comply with personal data protection standards.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>2. Data We Access</h2>
            <p>When you log in with your LINE account, we request access to the following data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Basic profile information</strong> — Display Name and profile picture</li>
                <li><strong>LINE User ID</strong> — A unique user identifier used to identify you in the system</li>
                <li><strong>Email</strong> — Only if you consent and your LINE account has a linked email</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. Purpose of Data Use</h2>
            <p>We use the data we access only for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Verify identity and create a user account in the system</li>
                <li>Display your name and profile picture within the Application</li>
                <li>Link your account to Chatbot Management usage permissions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We do not sell, share, or use this data for marketing purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Profile data is stored in a database on servers controlled by CNU</li>
                <li>The system uses HTTPS for all communication channels</li>
                <li>LINE Access Tokens are used only to retrieve profile data and are not stored permanently</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Sharing Data with Third Parties</h2>
            <p>
                We do not share your data with third parties, except where necessary to communicate with the LINE Platform API
                as part of the normal Login process, which is governed by the
                <a href="https://line.me/en/terms/policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LINE Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
            <p>You may:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Disconnect the Application at any time via <strong>LINE Settings → Connected Applications</strong></li>
                <li>Request that your data be deleted from the system by contacting us at the email below</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>7. Data Deletion</h2>
            <p>
                If you wish to delete all data associated with your account, please contact us at
                <a href="mailto:cnuprogrammer2021@gmail.com">cnuprogrammer2021@gmail.com</a>
                We will process your request within 30 business days.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
                If there are significant changes to this policy, we will notify you through the Application.
                Continued use of the Application after the effective date constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact:<br />
                <strong>CNU Chatbot Management System</strong><br />
                Email: <a href="mailto:cnuprogrammer2021@gmail.com">cnuprogrammer2021@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <div class="policy-footer">
            <a href="/" class="text-muted text-decoration-none small">&larr; Back to home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .policy-wrapper {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 32px 16px 48px;
    }

    .policy-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        padding: 40px 48px;
    }

    .policy-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        padding-bottom: 24px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    .policy-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #06C755;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .policy-meta {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #888;
        margin: 4px 0 0;
    }

    section {
        margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    section h2 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    section p, section li {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    section ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    section a {
        color: #06C755;
    }

    .policy-footer {
        margin-top: 32px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 600px) {
        .policy-card { padding: 24px 20px; }
        .policy-header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; }
    }
</style>
